name: SURVIVAL OVERGROWTH
description:
SURVIVAL RABBIT FIGHTING!

Become a fast ninja quick rabbit! Approach your enemies and fight them frontally or attack them from behind. Watch out for them, because they come in groups too not just alone. Try to get a higher score and overthrow your own records! After a while, you will see that you are becoming better and evolving your skills.


-movement system
-AI system
-beautiful graphics
